patthana23.33:4.1: Namicchattaniyataṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paccayā sammattaniyato kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.33:5.1: Namicchattaniyataṃ naakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paccayā micchattaniyato akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.33:6.1: Namicchattaniyataṃ naabyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca aniyato abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.33:6.3: Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha … pe … avigate cha.
